'''Grange Fell Church''' commonly refferd to by locals as '''The Fell Church''' is an [[Church of England]] church in the Grange Fell area of [[Grange-Over-Sands]], [[Cumbria]], England. Built in 1907, this small church is part of the parish of St. Paul Grange Over Sands, along with [[St Paul Parish Church, Grange-over-Sands|St Paul Parish Church]] in the town centre.<ref>[http://www.achurchnearyou.com/grange-fell-church/ A church near you]</ref>
